1
00:00:44,362 --> 00:00:49,137
=The Hidden Heir Ye Chen=
(Adapted from "The Peerless Son-in-Law")

2
00:00:49,650 --> 00:00:52,275
=Episode 11=

3
00:00:58,887 --> 00:01:00,950
(Zhang Ermao's Antique Shop)

4
00:01:02,880 --> 00:01:03,679
Alright.

5
00:01:04,240 --> 00:01:05,520
Since you're such a devoted son,

6
00:01:05,920 --> 00:01:07,359
I'll handle it myself.

7
00:01:07,600 --> 00:01:08,280
800 thousand.

8
00:01:08,450 --> 00:01:09,079
It's all yours.

9
00:01:10,000 --> 00:01:10,840
800 thousand?

10
00:01:11,319 --> 00:01:13,120
What were you two
whispering about out there?

11
00:01:13,280 --> 00:01:13,959
One million.

12
00:01:14,480 --> 00:01:15,239
I'll take it.

13
00:01:18,200 --> 00:01:19,890
You're here to cause trouble,
aren't you?

14
00:01:20,280 --> 00:01:21,079
I'm telling you,

15
00:01:21,079 --> 00:01:22,200
this piece is mine.

16
00:01:23,840 --> 00:01:24,560
Two million.

17
00:01:24,560 --> 00:01:25,239
Three million.

18
00:01:25,560 --> 00:01:26,660
No matter how high he goes,

19
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,560
I'll outbid him by one.

20
00:01:32,079 --> 00:01:32,640
Fine.

21
00:01:32,920 --> 00:01:33,719
You've got money.

22
00:01:33,959 --> 00:01:34,760
I give up.

23
00:01:35,159 --> 00:01:35,719
Great.

24
00:01:36,959 --> 00:01:37,799
Sir,

25
00:01:38,079 --> 00:01:39,239
it's three million and one.

26
00:01:39,599 --> 00:01:40,319
It's yours.

27
00:01:44,040 --> 00:01:44,840
Why are we running?

28
00:01:44,840 --> 00:01:46,879
Bring my item back!

29
00:01:47,719 --> 00:01:48,239
Look.

30
00:01:48,862 --> 00:01:50,512
(Zhang Ermao's Antique Shop)

31
00:01:53,425 --> 00:01:54,562
(Zhang Ermao's Antique Shop)

32
00:01:54,599 --> 00:01:56,000
What kind of lousy vase is this?

33
00:01:56,000 --> 00:01:57,200
It's worth over three million?

34
00:01:57,290 --> 00:01:58,840
It looks no different from any other.

35
00:02:00,275 --> 00:02:03,300
(Manufactured
by Suhang Ceramics Factory)

36
00:02:07,640 --> 00:02:08,239
This...

37
00:02:08,239 --> 00:02:09,319
This is Grandpa's real vase.

38
00:02:09,719 --> 00:02:10,519
What's going on?

39
00:02:12,400 --> 00:02:13,480
I'll send you a photo.

40
00:02:13,680 --> 00:02:14,639
I don't care

41
00:02:14,639 --> 00:02:16,199
if you source it or custom-make it,

42
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,599
but I need an identical vase.

43
00:02:17,879 --> 00:02:18,960
(Zhang Ermao's Antique Shop)
I've got a big deal for you.

44
00:02:19,025 --> 00:02:20,185
Want to make three million?

45
00:02:20,479 --> 00:02:21,280
How?

46
00:02:21,479 --> 00:02:23,439
Someone will bid higher
within five minutes.

47
00:02:23,560 --> 00:02:24,987
I'll push it to three million.

48
00:02:25,080 --> 00:02:26,400
You take two, and I'll take one.

49
00:02:26,759 --> 00:02:28,039
That good of a deal?

50
00:02:32,599 --> 00:02:33,719
You're impressive.

51
00:02:34,700 --> 00:02:37,120
Isn't that the idiot
who just paid three million for a fake?

52
00:02:37,120 --> 00:02:38,719
Yeah. He's got money.

53
00:02:39,039 --> 00:02:40,199
Ye Chen, stop right there!

54
00:02:42,639 --> 00:02:44,120
What do you think you're doing?

55
00:02:44,240 --> 00:02:45,280
How dare you mess with me?

56
00:02:45,639 --> 00:02:46,759
I didn't mess with you.

57
00:02:46,759 --> 00:02:47,840
You just misjudged it yourself.

58
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:48,719
Yeah, I misjudged it.

59
00:02:48,960 --> 00:02:50,080
I'll beat you to death today!

60
00:02:50,080 --> 00:02:50,800
Dad, split up and run!

61
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:51,360
Get him!

62
00:02:54,199 --> 00:02:54,680
Stop!

63
00:03:05,159 --> 00:03:05,719
Stop!

64
00:03:08,199 --> 00:03:08,680
Ye Chen!

65
00:03:08,680 --> 00:03:09,280
You!

66
00:03:09,800 --> 00:03:10,680
Ye Chen!

67
00:03:10,680 --> 00:03:11,319
Put me down!

68
00:03:11,599 --> 00:03:12,280
I was wrong!

69
00:03:13,280 --> 00:03:14,719
Trash belongs in the trash can.

70
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,479
Say that again!

71
00:03:15,719 --> 00:03:16,719
Get back here, Ye Chen!

72
00:03:16,879 --> 00:03:17,199
I...

73
00:03:18,439 --> 00:03:19,240
Let me out!

74
00:03:21,762 --> 00:03:23,789
I'm seriously losing it here!

75
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:24,840
Ye Chen!

76
00:03:25,360 --> 00:03:26,360
Slow down!

77
00:03:31,000 --> 00:03:31,730
Wait, who are you?

78
00:03:32,080 --> 00:03:32,879
Leave the item,

79
00:03:33,680 --> 00:03:34,479
and you can go.

80
00:03:35,319 --> 00:03:35,800
Go on, run!

81
00:03:36,000 --> 00:03:37,300
I'm telling you, my sister is here.

82
00:03:37,319 --> 00:03:38,120
You're dead!

83
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:42,919
That's some big talk.

84
00:03:54,919 --> 00:03:55,800
Wait!

85
00:03:56,050 --> 00:03:58,400
I'm telling you, she's the national
martial arts champion,

86
00:03:58,400 --> 00:03:59,000
a sixth-degree black belt.

87
00:03:59,000 --> 00:04:00,719
(Qin Aoxue, the Qin family's daughter)
Her nickname is Firecracker.

88
00:04:01,000 --> 00:04:02,159
You're finished!

89
00:04:02,900 --> 00:04:03,639
You're just a kid.

90
00:04:03,639 --> 00:04:04,720
I won't hold it against you.

91
00:04:04,730 --> 00:04:05,990
If you keep this up, I won't go easy!

92
00:04:06,800 --> 00:04:07,479
I'm warning you.

93
00:04:07,479 --> 00:04:08,680
Put the vase on the ground,

94
00:04:08,680 --> 00:04:09,680
bow your head, apologize,

95
00:04:09,680 --> 00:04:10,900
and maybe I will forgive you.

96
00:04:14,120 --> 00:04:15,039
I await your guidance.

97
00:04:19,400 --> 00:04:19,960
He ran off!

98
00:04:19,960 --> 00:04:20,890
What are you doing here?

99
00:04:28,639 --> 00:04:29,380
Is it real or not?

100
00:04:38,162 --> 00:04:38,722
Don't!

101
00:04:38,787 --> 00:04:39,375
(Hetian Seed Jade: 96,000)

102
00:04:39,399 --> 00:04:40,079
(Hetian Seed Jade)

103
00:04:40,759 --> 00:04:41,199
You...

104
00:04:42,160 --> 00:04:42,959
(Nanhai Agarwood: 65,000)
(Nanhai Agarwood)

105
00:04:44,079 --> 00:04:44,480
I...

106
00:04:45,120 --> 00:04:45,800
(Chicken Blood Stone: 18,000)
(Chicken Blood Stone)

107
00:04:47,800 --> 00:04:48,520
Are you done yet?

108
00:04:48,879 --> 00:04:50,079
- Hold it!
- Don't throw!

109
00:04:50,962 --> 00:04:52,250
(Piggy Bank: 10)

110
00:04:52,800 --> 00:04:53,199
This...

111
00:04:53,800 --> 00:04:54,839
Where are you going?

112
00:04:54,839 --> 00:04:55,439
After him!

113
00:04:56,839 --> 00:04:57,680
Stop right there!

114
00:04:59,759 --> 00:05:00,839
Leave the item!

115
00:05:00,839 --> 00:05:01,560
Stop!

116
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,560
Leave it!

117
00:05:04,560 --> 00:05:05,279
Stop!

118
00:05:07,120 --> 00:05:08,319
I cannot run anymore.

119
00:05:09,399 --> 00:05:10,079
I give up.

120
00:05:10,439 --> 00:05:11,959
You just want the vase, right?

121
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:13,120
I'll give it to you.

122
00:05:18,325 --> 00:05:22,040
(This story is purely fictional.)

123
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,390
Weren't you acting all cocky just now?

124
00:05:24,800 --> 00:05:25,480
Give it back.

125
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,480
I'm taking it.

126
00:05:32,199 --> 00:05:33,279
Mr. Ye is impressive.

127
00:05:33,800 --> 00:05:36,130
Was that the legendary
Sunflower Pressure Point technique?

128
00:05:36,300 --> 00:05:38,127
Looks like we didn't
even need to step in.

129
00:05:41,160 --> 00:05:42,279
Hey, what are you doing?

130
00:05:42,279 --> 00:05:42,800
Go after him!

131
00:05:43,319 --> 00:05:44,480
I am talking to you!

132
00:05:46,040 --> 00:05:46,600
What?

133
00:05:49,610 --> 00:05:51,279
Weren't you
the national martial arts champion?

134
00:05:51,279 --> 00:05:52,240
Weren't you some high level

135
00:05:52,240 --> 00:05:52,959
black belt?

136
00:05:53,279 --> 00:05:54,079
You're useless!

137
00:05:54,800 --> 00:05:55,959
I'm losing it!

138
00:06:03,000 --> 00:06:03,990
Who told you to film this!

139
00:06:04,040 --> 00:06:04,959
Stop filming!

140
00:06:04,959 --> 00:06:05,425
(Breaking: Woman in red causes a scene
on the street. Art or emergency?)

141
00:06:05,425 --> 00:06:05,687
(Woman goes crazy on the street.
Said to be a company exec. Come watch!)

142
00:06:05,687 --> 00:06:06,062
(Trending topic. Performance art.)

143
00:06:06,062 --> 00:06:06,512
(Pretty woman in red stands motionless.
Suspected alien prank.)

144
00:06:06,512 --> 00:06:07,287
(Shocking! Heiress of Huaying Pharma
performing in public.)

145
00:06:07,759 --> 00:06:08,720
I'm telling you,

146
00:06:09,240 --> 00:06:10,759
that girl from the Qin family

147
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:11,920
fights viciously.

148
00:06:12,639 --> 00:06:13,920
If I hadn't remembered the move

149
00:06:13,920 --> 00:06:15,450
Mr. Quan taught me,

150
00:06:16,199 --> 00:06:17,360
forget the vase.

151
00:06:17,759 --> 00:06:19,519
You wouldn't have even
seen a single shard.

152
00:06:29,250 --> 00:06:30,731
You touched the vase.

153
00:06:32,399 --> 00:06:33,519
Where is what was inside?

154
00:06:34,412 --> 00:06:35,212
Right here.

155
00:06:37,399 --> 00:06:39,240
A cold lifted base?

156
00:06:52,250 --> 00:06:54,199
I was worried
you would have trouble finding it,

157
00:06:54,639 --> 00:06:55,839
so I took it out in advance.

158
00:06:56,160 --> 00:06:57,290
Pretty considerate, isn't it?

159
00:07:01,839 --> 00:07:02,399
Mr. Ye,

160
00:07:03,279 --> 00:07:05,600
you really worked hard this time.

161
00:07:06,519 --> 00:07:08,240
It was nothing. No need to thank me.

162
00:07:09,079 --> 00:07:10,600
I've retrieved the formula for you,

163
00:07:11,360 --> 00:07:12,839
so I'm taking the vase.

164
00:07:13,560 --> 00:07:14,399
We had a deal.

165
00:07:14,959 --> 00:07:16,720
Once this was done, we were even.

166
00:07:16,780 --> 00:07:17,720
We go our separate ways.

167
00:07:18,639 --> 00:07:19,480
Hold on!

168
00:07:20,662 --> 00:07:21,650
(Please insert the remaining materials.)

169
00:07:22,560 --> 00:07:23,390
What does that mean?

170
00:07:23,720 --> 00:07:25,319
(Please insert the remaining materials.)
The prescription hidden inside the vase

171
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:28,160
is only part of your parents' formula.

172
00:07:28,360 --> 00:07:29,519
The remaining part

173
00:07:29,720 --> 00:07:31,519
should be in Qin Gang's hands.

174
00:07:32,399 --> 00:07:33,199
So you still

175
00:07:33,519 --> 00:07:35,279
need to keep looking for me.

176
00:07:35,680 --> 00:07:36,879
You must be joking.

177
00:07:37,100 --> 00:07:38,510
If you want it, go find it yourself.

178
00:07:38,650 --> 00:07:40,639
I've already
returned Old Mr. Xiao's prescription.

179
00:07:40,720 --> 00:07:41,720
I am done.

180
00:07:42,160 --> 00:07:42,800
Mr. Ye,

181
00:07:43,639 --> 00:07:45,720
that formula
was your parents' life's work.

182
00:07:46,000 --> 00:07:48,360
Don't you want
to see it restored as soon as possible?

183
00:07:48,920 --> 00:07:50,319
It might be very valuable.

184
00:07:50,920 --> 00:07:52,600
It might be very important.

185
00:07:52,600 --> 00:07:55,199
But what matters most to me
is my life with Churan.

186
00:07:55,519 --> 00:07:56,759
Freeze his black card.

187
00:07:57,050 --> 00:07:58,610
Sue him and demand immediate repayment.

188
00:07:58,610 --> 00:08:00,637
End all cooperation with the Xiao family.

189
00:08:02,639 --> 00:08:03,439
Sihai,

190
00:08:04,287 --> 00:08:05,812
I knew you were a sly fox

191
00:08:05,812 --> 00:08:07,075
who would not keep your promise.

192
00:08:08,800 --> 00:08:10,600
But you cannot control me anymore.

193
00:08:15,000 --> 00:08:16,519
Today I want to see

194
00:08:16,519 --> 00:08:18,439
how you plan to walk out of here.

195
00:08:20,600 --> 00:08:21,120
Oh right.

196
00:08:21,500 --> 00:08:22,600
I almost forgot to tell you.

197
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:26,040
I've already copied all the data
from the USB drive.

198
00:08:26,759 --> 00:08:28,199
You once told me

199
00:08:28,879 --> 00:08:30,600
my parents originally planned

200
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:32,270
to release the formula
to the public for free.

201
00:08:32,300 --> 00:08:33,639
All it takes is one click from me,

202
00:08:33,959 --> 00:08:35,519
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)
and it will be published immediately.

203
00:08:35,759 --> 00:08:36,720
Try me!

204
00:08:38,725 --> 00:08:39,275
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

205
00:08:40,625 --> 00:08:42,075
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

206
00:08:43,600 --> 00:08:45,187
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

207
00:08:47,187 --> 00:08:48,762
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

208
00:08:49,360 --> 00:08:50,960
Mr. Ye, please calm down.

209
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,710
If you keep pushing,
things will go wrong.

210
00:08:52,720 --> 00:08:53,919
The black card is mine.

211
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,987
Don't use Xiao Churan
to threaten me again.

212
00:08:57,650 --> 00:08:59,978
And don't ask me
to keep searching for the formula.

213
00:09:01,375 --> 00:09:02,237
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

214
00:09:03,250 --> 00:09:03,937
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

215
00:09:04,562 --> 00:09:05,487
(USB Drive Prescription Copy)

216
00:09:06,159 --> 00:09:06,840
Fine.

217
00:09:06,840 --> 00:09:07,690
I will do as you say.

218
00:09:09,260 --> 00:09:10,159
Thanks for cooperating.

219
00:09:10,679 --> 00:09:11,960
Next time you're fighting,

220
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,799
don't involve me.

221
00:09:16,600 --> 00:09:17,000
Hello?

222
00:09:17,240 --> 00:09:18,080
Dad is back already.

223
00:09:18,080 --> 00:09:18,960
How is it on your end?

224
00:09:19,090 --> 00:09:20,600
Did Qin Aodong give you any trouble?

225
00:09:20,700 --> 00:09:22,590
If things get out of hand,
we can call the police.

226
00:09:22,600 --> 00:09:23,990
I've got the medicine bottle with me.

227
00:09:24,639 --> 00:09:25,639
It has a small chip.

228
00:09:26,000 --> 00:09:26,990
I'll find someone to fix it.

229
00:09:27,360 --> 00:09:28,039
Go to bed early.

230
00:09:28,039 --> 00:09:28,890
Don't wait up for me.

231
00:09:29,759 --> 00:09:30,320
Okay.

232
00:09:31,399 --> 00:09:33,679
Mr. Ye, are you
looking for a restoration master?

233
00:09:34,120 --> 00:09:35,400
Do you need me to call someone?

234
00:09:36,150 --> 00:09:37,960
This is cold lift base removal
craftsmanship.

235
00:09:38,480 --> 00:09:40,519
Only a true expert
among experts can handle it.

236
00:09:41,020 --> 00:09:43,310
But we probably cannot
find someone like that on short notice.

237
00:09:43,320 --> 00:09:44,360
How do you plan

238
00:09:44,519 --> 00:09:46,039
to explain this to your wife?

239
00:09:46,700 --> 00:09:47,799
I will have to do it myself.

240
00:09:48,600 --> 00:09:50,320
Sihai, here is what we will do.

241
00:09:51,000 --> 00:09:52,180
Lend me your place for a bit.

242
00:09:52,450 --> 00:09:53,720
And you, make me a cup of coffee.

243
00:10:01,125 --> 00:10:04,115
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

244
00:10:04,559 --> 00:10:08,279
(Do you remember
the restoration technique I taught you?)

245
00:10:11,060 --> 00:10:14,060
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

246
00:10:14,300 --> 00:10:17,380
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

247
00:10:17,525 --> 00:10:20,805
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

248
00:10:21,025 --> 00:10:24,650
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

249
00:10:24,650 --> 00:10:27,875
♪I belong to no one♪

250
00:10:27,875 --> 00:10:31,050
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

251
00:10:31,137 --> 00:10:34,350
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

252
00:10:34,350 --> 00:10:38,875
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪

253
00:10:39,480 --> 00:10:41,240
Mr. Ye, this was incredible.

254
00:10:41,639 --> 00:10:43,399
We cannot even tell it was repaired.

255
00:10:49,840 --> 00:10:51,000
Mr. Tang, I'm heading out.

256
00:10:51,010 --> 00:10:51,720
Don't bother me.

257
00:10:55,639 --> 00:10:56,320
Mr. Tang,

258
00:10:57,000 --> 00:10:58,360
please don't be upset with Mr. Ye.

259
00:10:59,200 --> 00:10:59,919
Upset?

260
00:11:00,559 --> 00:11:01,840
Why would I be upset?

261
00:11:02,440 --> 00:11:04,200
The wolf cub I raised

262
00:11:04,679 --> 00:11:06,000
has finally grown up.

263
00:11:06,519 --> 00:11:08,039
I could not be happier.

264
00:11:08,799 --> 00:11:09,480
Are we

265
00:11:09,879 --> 00:11:11,080
still sending the video?

266
00:11:11,440 --> 00:11:12,200
Of course.

267
00:11:12,759 --> 00:11:14,320
He thinks he can get rid of me?

268
00:11:15,039 --> 00:11:16,519
It won't be that easy.

269
00:11:35,700 --> 00:11:38,188
♪They said I was only meant
to gaze at the light♪

270
00:11:38,275 --> 00:11:42,028
♪Never knowing I am the flame itself♪

271
00:11:42,488 --> 00:11:47,425
♪I am fireworks, not a fire cast aside♪

272
00:11:47,588 --> 00:11:49,875
♪I open my eyes amid the ruins♪

273
00:11:50,188 --> 00:11:52,868
♪No one shields me
from the wind or the sky♪

274
00:11:53,938 --> 00:11:56,563
♪Let them mock, let them sneer♪

275
00:11:56,863 --> 00:11:59,875
♪I sharpen my silence into blades♪

276
00:12:00,075 --> 00:12:03,125
♪Every cold word, I remember♪

277
00:12:03,238 --> 00:12:06,200
♪Etching my path of defiance
into my heart♪

278
00:12:06,468 --> 00:12:09,625
♪Fate did not sign my future for me♪

279
00:12:09,850 --> 00:12:13,600
♪I carved my own light
with clenched fists♪

280
00:12:13,600 --> 00:12:16,463
♪I belong to no one♪

281
00:12:16,525 --> 00:12:19,975
♪I am the ember
that refuses to bow to destiny♪

282
00:12:19,975 --> 00:12:22,650
♪Even if the world burns me into ash♪

283
00:12:22,650 --> 00:12:28,988
♪I will rise upon those ashes♪
